channel.title: Myths and Legends of the Great Plains by Katharine Berry Judson (1866 - 1929)
channel.description: Myths and Legends of the Great Plains is a compendium of myths and legends from the Great Plains region of the US. It includes many short stories, and also quite a few songs and poems. Each tale is tagged with what culture it is from - (Summary by Kyle Van De Glast)
